1
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:52,520
This Cangyue,

2
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:53,840
when she first arrived,

3
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:55,920
wanted to find a chance to seduce His Majesty.

4
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:58,240
I didn't expect her to actually succeed.

5
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:01,560
I guess she will be a concubine soon.

6
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:03,560
Our small maid's room

7
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:05,720
can no longer accommodate a big shot like her.

8
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:07,000
That's right.

9
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,860
His Majesty is so temperamental.

10
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:11,480
In case she doesn't come back alive,

11
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:14,520
let's quickly pack her things and throw them out

12
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:16,200
to get rid of the bad luck.

13
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:18,800
Cangyue.

14
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,760
Oh, you're back.

15
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:25,840
Don't tell me you slept with him for a night

16
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,720
and got nothing in return.

17
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,039
What are you doing?

18
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:32,320
What are we doing?

19
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,720
Telling you to get out.

20
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:36,120
We don't have room for a vixen like you here.

21
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:37,759
Throw her stuff out.

22
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:39,780
I'd like to see you try.

23
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:44,200
Why wouldn't we?

24
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,560
Teach her a good lesson.

25
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,280
Mom!

26
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,240
Mom.

27
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,040
Apologize to me.

28
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:34,079
I'm sorry.

29
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:35,160
Louder.

30
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:37,520
I'm sorry.

31
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,480
It seems

32
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,280
it's time to teach you some rules.

33
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,160
Have you all learned?

34
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,600
Yes.

35
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:04,840
At ease.

36
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:05,820
Attention.

37
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,090
Parade rest.

38
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:13,320
Count off! 1 2 3 4 5 6.

39
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:17,400
My college military training wasn't in vain.

40
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,440
[Coughing]

41
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,090
Paying respects to Eunuch Sun.

42
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:31,000
Paying respects to Eunuch Sun.

43
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:39,960
How was it at His Majesty's palace last night?

44
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,240
Not bad.

45
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,440
Get ready.

46
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:48,120
You're on duty for His Majesty tonight.

47
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:52,480
I see you caught His Majesty's eye,

48
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:54,320
so I'm looking out for you.

49
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,720
Seize the opportunity.

50
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:57,079
And for wealth and glory,

51
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:59,040
you'll never have to worry again.

52
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,380
Thank you, Eunuch Sun.

53
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,560
Your Majesty.

54
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,690
Didn't I tell you to get out?

55
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:24,490
I am here to serve you for your bath and change of clothes.

56
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:28,720
Cang Yue.

57
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,520
Did Eunuch Sun send you?

58
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,120
Yes.

59
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:44,960
This time, a different one has arrived.

60
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,000
Take them off.

61
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,260
Why are you so slow?

62
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,760
I thought someone who wasn't afraid of me had come,

63
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:20,160
but I didn't expect you came to take my life.

64
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:24,000
My aunt's tricks are getting more and more clever.

65
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,440
You deserve to die.

66
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,160
Why?

67
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,960
How dare you ask such a thing?

68
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:31,600
I am the Holy Maiden of the Moon Shadow Clan.

69
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,520
We, the people of the Moon Shadow Clan,

70
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:36,920
are indifferent to fame and wealth, and aloof from the world.

71
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,880
I lived happily every day.

72
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,520
My parents treated me very well.

73
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,720
They were kind-hearted.

74
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:59,040
Later, I heard you ordered the slaughter of my entire clan

75
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,640
and the murder of my parents.

76
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,120
You really are the Holy Maiden of the Yueying Clan.

77
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,000
Yes.

78
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,440
What happened to the Yueying Clan?

79
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:15,700
Is anyone still alive?

80
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,920
They are all dead.

81
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,040
As far as the eye could see.

82
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,240
Corpses everywhere.

83
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,800
What are you laughing at?

84
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,280
Forget it.

85
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,320
Kill me if you want.

86
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,400
Don't you want revenge?

87
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,450
I will give you a chance.

88
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,400
Only one chance.

89
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,250
Why aren't you doing it?

90
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,320
That's not right.

91
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,920
Don't the characters I kill in this game

92
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,450
disappear automatically?

93
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,400
How could they?

94
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,640
Hello, player.

95
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:19,520
Key character death detected.

96
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:22,050
The plot point has been automatically reset.

97
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,640
This is reloading a save.

98
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,380
I killed the wrong person.

99
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,920
Don't you want revenge?

100
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,330
I will give you a chance.

101
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,360
Let me try again.

102
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,520
Only one chance.

103
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,720
Warning.

104
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,520
There are only two reset chances.

105
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,960
If the plot is interrupted again,

106
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:49,360
the experience will be terminated immediately.

107
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,720
Don't you want revenge?

108
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,250
I will give you a chance.

109
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:57,540
I'll only give you one chance.

110
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,250
Are you still not making your move?

111
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:10,800
You are not going to kill me?

112
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:14,000
I believe Your Majesty did not wipe out the Yueying Tribe.

113
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,120
I just want to know

114
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:18,360
who is the mastermind behind this.

115
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:22,720
Experiencer's task objective is 25% complete.

116
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,980
You don't need to know.

117
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,920
Since you are a daughter of the Yueying Tribe,

118
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:28,240
I will send someone to escort you out of the palace

119
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,500
to keep you safe for the rest of your life.

120
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,169
But I want to know the truth.

121
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,400
Your Majesty.

122
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,039
You know the truth.

123
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,600
I don't.

124
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,440
After all this,

125
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,700
the target of revenge isn't Si Xingxuan.

126
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:47,720
Then who is it?

127
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:50,920
Oh, Miss Cangyue.

128
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,720
Eunuch Sun.

129
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,280
Rubik's Cube.
